summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Thirty-second Avenue form the north line of Albion Heights Addition to East Howell Street et al in the City of Seattle, by grading under Ordinance No. 19848, creating Local Improvement District No. 1930 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
